OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775578269
OL,3,CRescue mission after car flips doing
OL,4,C'doughnuts' on beach
OL,6,FA person has been injured after a
OL,7,Fdriver performing "doughnuts" on the
OL,8,Fbeach flipped their vehicle - sparking
OL,9,Fa multi-agency rescue operation.
OL,11,FTeams from Furness Coastguard and
OL,12,FArnside Coastguard were called to
OL,13,FFlookburgh in Cumbria on Easter Monday.
OL,15,FThe driver had reportedly been driving
OL,16,Fon the sand when the wheels caught,
OL,17,Fcausing the vehicle to dig in and flip
OL,18,Fonto its side.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
