PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775578269
OL,3,CRescue mission after car flips doing
OL,4,C'doughnuts' on beach
OL,6,FThe initial call to the Rescue
OL,7,FCoordination Centre in Holyhead
OL,8,Fsparked a major multi-agency response,
OL,9,Fas it was initially unclear if anyone
OL,10,Fwas trapped or injured.
OL,12,FOne casualty was treated at the scene
OL,13,Fby fire crews before being handed over
OL,14,Fto paramedics for further care, the
OL,15,Fcoastguard said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
