FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775578269
OL,3,CRescue mission after car flips doing
OL,4,C'doughnuts' on beach
OL,6,FThe crashed vehicle posed a
OL,7,Fsignificant pollution risk to the
OL,8,Flocal environment, a spokesperson
OL,9,Fadded, as Flookburgh is designated as
OL,10,Fa Site of Special Scientific Interest
OL,11,F(SSSI).
OL,13,FWith the help of Bay Search and Rescue
OL,14,F(BaySar), the car was removed from the
OL,15,Fbeach to prevent fuel or oil leaks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
